Well hello there group. Your probably wondering where the hell I've 
been. Ya see, I'm in the process of moving and my internet has been 
cut off, as well as cable tv...*sigh* Anyway I havn't been able to 
get on and do anything in any RPG, forum or anything else I'm 
involved with online. I'm only on now because I managed to get on a 
friends comp. Hopefully I'll be online soon after the move. It's 
going to be a few weeks though. If you havn't done something already 
with my charrs then the other council members should take them. If 
you feel you need to find a council replacment for me then do so. I 
miss RPing and everyone here. Untill next time NBW. Peace!

~RoboRick
